            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:1c4372c9-a83c-4aad-938c-a07f009a7cd2</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/overall_equipment_effectiveness/~3/_1b4p3WiNuU/overall-equipment-effectiveness</link>
